  <brief_title>Predictive Variables of the Hemodynamic Effect During the Laparoscopic Surgery in Children</brief_title>
  <acronym>Lapa-BP</acronym>
  <official_title>Study on the Predictive Variables Able to Predict the Hemodynamic Effect of Intra-abdominal Pressure in the Children Undergoing Laparoscopic Surgery</official_title>
